{"tid":398742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"妻拒骨癌姑仔同住 驚間屋死人唔值錢 與夫隔空網上駁火","createTime":"2017-09-13T11:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T12:10:49.000Z","uid":22349,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e677c43b7832f3cecbe3668926f27fcea30f0a1","tid":398742,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T11:56:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170913/bkn-20170913150125322-0913_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170913%2Fbkn-20170913150125322-0913_00822_001.html&d=K%2BrjvxT0%2FZuN7sZZp0RS3I9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=8a36b994\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170913/bkn-20170913150125322-0913_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2017-09-13<br />\n<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=K%2BrjvxT0%2FZuN7sZZp0RS3I9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=a4844603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a><br />\n<br />\n家家有本難唸的經。近日Facebook流傳一則「我老婆唔俾(畀)我呀(阿)妹翻(返)屋企」貼文，事件男女主角更一度在不同網上論壇隔空駁火，互數對方不是，引起網民廣泛回響。事緣一名自稱25歲的男子，早前於網上論壇發文指在新婚不久發現17歲的妹妹患骨癌，其妻竟以「不想在死過人嘅屋度過世」、「屋死過人就唔值錢」等藉口，拒絕從醫院接妹妹回家同住休養。<br />\n<br />\n男事主指，早在英國讀書與妻子結識時，已知妻子當時與妹妹交惡，其妻經常借題發揮指摘他「幫住曬(晒)個妹」和要脅(挾)分手，但沒想到今次妻子竟會因妹妹患病的事，搬返娘家。事主直言認為妻子「今鋪玩大咗」，令他十分有衝動要離婚。<br />\n<br />\n其妻得悉該貼文後，亦不遑多讓在另一論壇以「發現老公在某討論區唱衰我」發文，指摘男方在結婚後性情大變，感到自己不再重要。惟女方貼文後被網民圍剿，最後終刪除貼文。"},{"pid":"7102efc82a6b2be5d4f811acc8b34f5ffa4541e3","tid":398742,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T11:59:30.000Z","msg":"臭雞港女不意外"},{"pid":"7bfca16495e4eb73fa32390275956eaa2d6d78c8","tid":398742,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T11:59:55.000Z","msg":"正一閪女人黎"},{"pid":"87fff6f0e4cac6b241f231a138106f307975846c","tid":398742,"uid":93752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:00:15.000Z","msg":"上網新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96f02c241623da2baaf4d166af451baf0b25b3a7","tid":398742,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:00:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁又有新聞"},{"pid":"07ccc3f46bbae33050914e15179dad7ab3f0a023","tid":398742,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:02:54.000Z","msg":"喺lihkg見過"},{"pid":"1a1b0312ae343caa13e77febcd74cc882e163cb4","tid":398742,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:03:33.000Z","msg":"唔係雖遠必豬咩？做乜又攞料寫新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ce305f1235a03b4c5d1829d3c8c9e71ff86e1b","tid":398742,"uid":35276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:03:48.000Z","msg":"diu係咪條八婆咁搞鳩托巴？"},{"pid":"4379286403598a9ad37d3b2e38cb4c7b1ecddf1b","tid":398742,"uid":67346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:04:02.000Z","msg":"仆街東方<br />\n呢啲新聞俾拓也巴啊妹睇到會更怪責自己"},{"pid":"268705a6d3e55cfb9ee78b171bdafb8b25ad053d","tid":398742,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:05:57.000Z","msg":"第日老公有病又唔比佢返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55036d8aecbd4043792582e82071f8594352c0b","tid":398742,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:10:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170913/bkn-20170913150125322-0913_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170913%2Fbkn-20170913150125322-0913_00822_001.html&d=K%2BrjvxT0%2FZuN7sZZp0RS3I9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=8a36b994\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170913/bkn-20170913150125322-0913_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2017-09-13<br />\n<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.